* 支持 [[超高畫質電視|8K]]、5K、[[4K解析度|4K]]、[[超高畫質電視|UHD]]、[[2K解析度|2K]]、HD(最大1920x1080)和SD分辨率。<ref name=":1">{{Cite web |url=https://www.apple.com/final-cut-pro/docs/Apple_ProRes_White_Paper.pdf |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-02-28 |archive-date=2021-04-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210416090321/https://www.apple.com/final-cut-pro/docs/Apple_ProRes_White_Paper.pdf }}</ref>
